DOWNFALL-CLONE.description:
Choose a card.
Place a copy of that card into [gold]Stasis[/gold].{IfUpgraded:show:
[gold]Accelerate[/gold].|}

DOWNFALL-COWER.description:
Gain {Block:diff()} Block.
Add a *Hole {IfUpgraded:show:*Up+|[gold]Up} to your {IfUpgraded:show:hand.|hand[/gold].}
Exhaust.

DOWNFALL-FLARE_FLICK.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage.
[gold]Ignite[/gold] the current Ghostflame.{IfUpgraded:show:
You may choose to [gold]Advance[/gold] or [gold]Retract[/gold].|}

DOWNFALL-GLITTERING_GAMBIT.description:
Unplayable.{IfUpgraded:show: Ethereal.|}
Cannot be removed from your deck.
[gold]Gift[/gold]: Upgraded Rare and {GlitteringGambitPower:diff()} Gold.

DOWNFALL-LACERATE.description:
Apply {LaceratePower:diff()} [gold]Venom to ALL enemies[/gold].
Gain a *Crippling {IfUpgraded:show:*Cloud+.|[gold]Cloud[/gold].}
Exhaust.

DOWNFALL-ONE_TWO_COMBO.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage.
{IfUpgraded:show:[gold]Command twice[/gold].|[gold]Command[/gold].}
When you [gold]Split[/gold], return this from the discard pile to your hand.

DOWNFALL-OVEREXERT.description:
Gain 5 [gold]Potency[/gold].{IfUpgraded:show:
[gold]Command twice[/gold].|}
{OverexertPower:diff()} turns from now, [gold]Absorb all Slimes[/gold].

DOWNFALL-PREPARE.description:
{IfUpgraded:show:|Gain {Block:diff()} Block.
}Next turn, gain {energyPrefix:energyIcons(1)} and draw {PreparePower:diff()} cards.
{IfUpgraded:show:Retain up to {PreparePower:diff()} cards this turn. |}Exhaust.

DOWNFALL-RAIN_OF_DICE.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage.
[gold]Muddle a card[/gold], then add *Rain *of {IfUpgraded:show:*Dice+|[gold]Dice} to your {IfUpgraded:show:hand.|hand[/gold].}
Exhaust.

DOWNFALL-REPLICATION.description:
Choose a card.
{IfUpgraded:show:Gain|Put} a copy {IfUpgraded:show:|on top }of {IfUpgraded:show:it.|your draw pile.}
Exhaust.

DOWNFALL-THROWING_CARDS.description:
Add X copies of {IfUpgraded:show:*FTL+|[gold]FTL} to your {IfUpgraded:show:hand.|hand[/gold].}
Gain {energyPrefix:energyIcons(1)}.
Exhaust.

DOWNFALL-WHACK.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage.
Add a {IfUpgraded:show:*Wallop+|[gold]Wallop} to your {IfUpgraded:show:hand.|hand[/gold].}
Exhaust.
